column5: Just wanted to shout a Happy B-Day to FishnSled! Happy 50th bud! WIll and Cliff are out today plying the waters of Lake O last I heard.... hope yah get a "fifty" today! LOL HH
Happy birthday to you, Will! Have a super day.
50??????????? I thought he was like 40ish.  Happy Bday Will.
Happy Birthday Will, all the best to ya !!
Happy birthday amigoâ€¦..have a GREAT DAY!
Happy birthday bud And remember you're not getting older you're getting -------na. You're getting  older lol. Almost catching up to me.
Happy birthday Will, this is a milestone.
No better way to spend you're 50th than on the water... well there is, but... have a great day anyhow Will !!
Happy 50th Will !All the best to you my friend
Happy 50th Will, looks like you were born 6 days before me
Have a good one sir!Happy Birthday!To be 50 again,lol!!
Happy Birthday Will!! Had a great day out on the water as usual!

Shhhhhhhh.....  trying to keep the 50 thing a secret.....LOL!  Thanks everyone!  A fun day on the water is what the doctor ordered.  It was to be Lake O but with the winds in the forecast we headed to the Kawarthas for some pike.  Found some sweet water with warmer temps and a couple of fish made their way to the boat along with a few swing and misses.  Not a bad way to spend the day at all.  Didn't even see another boat! Don't think I've ever had a day like that in the Kawarthas.  Great having you along for the maiden voyage Cliff!
Ooops ! A day behind schedule, but hope it was a super day for you Will. Happy Birthday ! Cheers !!!
